body:
I encountered an issue when running a big project. The code is:
`VL_CONCATWWW(104192,103936,256,__Vtemp340, __Vtemp339, data)`
The error report is 
**Thread 7 received signal SIGSEGV, Segmentation fault.
[Switching to Thread 0x155550701640 (LWP 2561160)]
__memmove_avx512_unaligned_erms () at../sysdeps/x86_64/multiarch/memmove - vec - unaligned - erms.S:708**
I have done some debug, the code itself is fine. The problem is in function _vl_insert_WW:
