For the code **for (int i = 0; i < (words - 1); ++i) iowp[lword + i] = lwp[i];** , the clang++ compiler will transfer this part to memmove-vec-unaligned  to realize, it is very likely a problem of memory alignment or out-of-bound.  What can be done to solve this problem？

